front.title: Sleen
front.gametext: Ferocity = destiny - 3. Habitat: planet sites (except Hoth and Tatooine) and Dark Waters. Cumulatively absorbs (temporarily cancels) one [Light Side Force] icon present. Parasite: None.
front.lore: Slow, omnivorous swamp forager. Eats insects. Seeks damp, dark environments strong with the Force.

canceledBy: Ounee Ta (V) - Defensive Shield prevents Sleen from canceling Force icons
